---
title: Toasted Thai Rice Bowl with Shrimp, Sweet Corn, and Red Bell Pepper
description: Chili, lime, and soy sauce pack a delicious flavor punch in this Thai-inspired shrimp stir-fry. The toasted rice adds a nutty flavor and textural contrast to round out the dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/565f1f75f8b25ebf518b4567.jpg
